<div class="modal-black-content"><span class="close"><span class="close-black-modal">×</span></span>
<h4>AT HORIZON MEDIA, DIVERSITY, EQUITY AND INCLUSION IS OUR DNA</h4>

<p>We are committed to being a true organization of belonging by creating an enlightened work environment that reflects our diverse and unique communities.</p>

<p>We will cultivate an environment where everyone has equitable access to learning and advancement and where our diverse community of employees are nurtured, celebrated and empowered to be their authentic selves.</p>

<p>This commitment requires us to evolve in ways that will be challenging and - at times - uncomfortable. However, nothing worth doing is ever easy and we believe there is no more worthy an effort than this.</p>

<p>We are excited to share this journey with our clients, partners, employees – and you.</p>

<p>Watch this space.</p>
